THe '''Palais de Justice''' station  is located on [[Bordeaux Tramway Line A|line]] [[Image:Logo Ligne A.png|20px]] of the [[tramway de Bordeaux]].

==Situation==
The station is located by [[Alphonse Juin|Mar<U+00E9>chal Juin]] Boulevard in [[Bordeaux]]. The change to [[ground-level power supply]] (APS) at this station allows an absence of [[overhead line]]s in downtown Bordeaux.

